            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Kia 亚太区近日于台湾举办 2024 年 Kia EV 日，展示多款电动车产品及概念车型，当中包括首次于亚太区首次展示 Kia EV3、全新概念车 PV5 及 EV4。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/acloserlookatthetoda.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275768" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/acloserlookatthetoda-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/acloserlookatthetoda-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/acloserlookatthetoda.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aglimpseofthefutureo.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aglimpseofthefutureo-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aglimpseofthefutureo-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aglimpseofthefutureo.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Kia 自 2021 年品牌重塑后采取极简主义，旨在激发电动车革命。Kia 亚太区首席执行官 Ki Seok Ahn 表示首届亚太区 EV 日代表 Kia 对可持续移动的坚定承诺及推动电动车革命的坚定步伐，将展示 Kia 的电动车技术、创新设计和精心策划的战略。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mrkiseokahnpresident-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275709" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mrkiseokahnpresident-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mrkiseokahnpresident-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mrkiseokahnpresident-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>首次于亚太区展示的 Kia EV3 将旗舰车款 SUV EV9 的创新技术引入紧凑型电动 SUV 领域，并承袭 Kia 以往电动车的创新与技术，以满足入门级紧凑型电动 SUV 市场的需求。Kia EV3 采用 Opposites United 设计理念，具备方正的后轮拱设计、流线型车顶及坚固的车身姿态，呈现出现代运动风格，预计 2025 年于亚太区部分国家推出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_fn.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_fn-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_fn-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_fn.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_01.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_01-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_01-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kia_ev3_keyvisual_01.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Kia EV3 搭载最新的驾驶技术，基于 E-GMP（电动全球模组化平台）构建，并配备电动动态扭矩矢量控制（eDTVC），以实现最佳牵引力。此外，EV3 还拥有多项先进驾驶辅助系统（ADAS），包括前方碰撞预防辅助系统 2、车道保持辅助系统、高速公路驾驶辅助系统 2、倒车碰撞预防辅助系统及远程智慧泊车辅助系统。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668413-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668413-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668413-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668413-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668407-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668407-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668407-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/668407-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_01-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_01-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_01-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_01-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_02-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_02-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_03-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_03-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_03-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev3_gtl_03-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外，Kia 亦于场内展示概念车 EV4 及首次于亚太区亮相的概念车 PV5。EV4 概念车体现了「Opposites United」设计理念中的「Power to Progress」，融合自然元素与尖端技术，呈现出引人注目的轮廓及宽敞的驾驶座设计，并展现了全新类型的电动轿车。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651719-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651719-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651719-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651719-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651745-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651745-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651745-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651745-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651746-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651746-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651746-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651746-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651747-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651747-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651747-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/651747-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PV5 概念车则是 Kia 首款专属的「Platform Beyond Vehicle」（PBV），提供整体的移动解决方案，融入空间感与软件技术，超越传统车辆。PV5 概念车的设计考虑到了多元化需求，从商务用途到冒险活动均能应对自如，其坚固简洁的设计专注于提供可定制化的多用途车型，可满足不同驾驶需要。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275758" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5rinterior-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5rinterior-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5rinterior-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5rinterior-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275760" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5interior1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5exterior1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275762" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5exterior1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5exterior1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv5exterior1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv1_pv5hrexteriordoc-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv1_pv5hrexteriordoc-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv1_pv5hrexteriordoc-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pv1_pv5hrexteriordoc-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pbvlineup_rev-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pbvlineup_rev-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pbvlineup_rev-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/pbvlineup_rev-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>同属首次亮相的 Kia 旗舰电动 LSUV EV9 早在全球范围内赢得了广泛的认可与殊荣，包括 2024 年「世界女性年度风云车」总冠军及 2024 年「世界年度风云车」、「世界年度最佳电动车」等车坛大奖的多项荣誉。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint01_krver2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275742" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint01_krver2-694x370.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint01_krver2-694x370.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint01_krver2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint02_krver2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275743" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint02_krver2-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint02_krver2-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvint02_krver2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvext01_krver2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275744" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvext01_krver2-694x466.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvext01_krver2-694x466.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9gtlkvext01_krver2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9kvgt03on2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275745" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9kvgt03on2-694x449.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="449" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9kvgt03on2-694x449.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ev9kvgt03on2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mv_24my_ge_lhd_exter-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275746" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mv_24my_ge_lhd_exter-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mv_24my_ge_lhd_exter-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mv_24my_ge_lhd_exter-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Kia EV3 规格：</p><p>车身尺寸：4,300 毫米 x 1,850 毫米 x 1,560 毫米<br />
纯电续航里程 (WLTP)：长续航版：605 公里 / 短续航版：436 公里</p><p>电池容量：长续航版：81.4 千瓦时 / 短续航版：58.3 千瓦时</p><p>Kia EV4 规格：</p><p>车身尺寸：4,730 毫米 x 1,860 毫米 x 1,480 毫米</p><p>纯电续航里程 (WLTP)： 长续航版：630 公里 / 短续航版：430 公里</p><p>电池容量： 长续航版：81.4 千瓦时 / 短续航版：58.3 千瓦时</p><p>Kia EV5 规格：</p><p>车身尺寸：4,615 毫米 x 1,875 毫米 x 1,715 毫米</p><p>纯电续航里程 (WLTP)： 长续航版：555 公里 / 短续航版：400 公里</p><p>电池容量： 长续航版：88.1 千瓦时 / 短续航版：64.2 千瓦时</p><p>Kia EV9 规格：</p><p>车身尺寸：5,010 毫米 x 1,980 毫米 x 1,750 毫米</p><p>纯电续航里程 (WLTP)： 长续航版：563 公里 / 短续航版：443 公里</p><p>电池容量： 长续航版：99.8 千瓦时 / 短续航版：76.1 千瓦时</p><p>Kia PV5 规格：</p><p>车身尺寸： 4,700 毫米 x 1,850 毫米 x 1,900 毫米</p><p>纯电续航里程 (WLTP)： 长续航版：约 400 公里 / 短续航版：约 200 公里</p><p>电池容量： 长续航版：约 70 千瓦时 / 短续航版：约 40 千瓦时</p><br /><b>
